            "1. TO’UTUPU ‘O TONGA KE MOU FANONGO FAKA’ANAUA NI MEI HE LOLOTO (2X) KE KALAISI’IA ‘ETEU NOFO ‘O TUHA MO TAAU MO HONO FINANGALO MO’ONI ‘A E TOHI LAU ‘A E POTO MO’UI ‘APASIA KAE MA’U ‘A E ‘ILO \n\n 2. MO’UI MA’A KALAISI FAI HONO TALAKI TO’UTUPU ‘O TONGA FOKI KI HE ‘EIKI (2X) LUSEFA ‘ENA MOE FILI LAHI TE NE ‘AUHANI ‘A E MO’UI VAIVAI KO HO TA MALU’I KOE LOTU MOE HUFAKI PEA KE ‘APASIA ‘O PIKI KI HONO KOLOSI \n\n 3. SOTOMA MO KOMOLA HONO ‘AUHA’ANGA MO’UI FAKALUSA HOTAU FA’AHINGA LOMAKI VAI TO HE KUONGA ‘O NOA TANGI MO KAILA E KAU ANGAHALA FOKI MAI A (BASS) FOKI MAI A PEA MEI HO ‘ALUNGA \n\n TAU SI’I ‘AUHE TO’UTUPU ‘O TONGA TUI A MU’A TAMA KI HE ‘OTUA KE KALAISI’IA ‘A HOTAU ANGA KA TAU HAO MEI HE MATE TA’ENGATA \n\n SISU E KE KE PUKENIMA AU TAKI ATU AU SI HAO MAMATA HE KO AU ‘ENI KO E HIA MATEA NA’E PAU KI HE MATE TA’ENGATA KAU HAO ATU ‘I HO TA’ATA’A (BASS) NA’E TAFE MEI HO VAKAVAKA KOE HUHU’I ‘O ‘ETAU ANGAHALA (BASS) KO E HUFANGA’ANGA E TANGATA"),
    Book(
        number: "210",
        title: 'KO E FOLOFOLA ‘A E ‘OTUA KIA NOA',
        content:
            "1. KOE FOLOFOLA ‘A E ‘OTUA KIA NOA KE NE FA’U ‘A E ‘A’AKE ONGO KI HE LANGI ‘A E KOVI ‘A MAMANI PEA KUOPAU KE VETEKI ‘A E NOFO NI \n\n 2. NOA KE KE NGAOHI HA’O ‘A’AKE HE KUOPAU KE U LOMAKI ‘A E FONUA FAKAHU KI AI ‘A E MANU KOTOA PE HU KI AI FOKI MO HO FAMILI \n\n 3. NE PATUKI PE ‘A NOA ‘I HE ‘A’AKE KAE FAI HONO LUMA’I MO HONO TAUKAE A’U KI HE ‘AHO KUO TO MAI ‘A E LOMAKI KI HE FONUA TANGI SI’I KAKAI HE KUMI MO’UI \n\n TAU NOA E ‘OFA HE’EMAU TANGI PEA KE ‘OUA ‘E FETONGI E KOVI ‘ALO’OFA KI HE’EMAU MO’UI KUO TAPUNI ‘A E MATAPA KUO LOMAKI ‘A E FONUA NOA E TO’O ‘A E MATAPA"),
    Book(
        number: "211",
        title: '  KO E NOFO ‘AUHE ‘I HE FONUA KO MOAPE',
        content:
            "1. KOE NOFO ‘AUHE ‘I HE FONUA KO MOAPE NAOMI MO ‘ELIMELEKI MALONI PEA MO KILIONI KOE ONGO FEFINE MOAPE KO ‘O’OPA MO LUTE KO E ONGO UAIFI ‘A E ONGO TAMA ‘A NAOMI NE HOKO ‘A PULE ‘A MATE KE NE VA’ETU’UA SI’ENAU NOFO HOPOATE \n\n 2. KOE TOKI ME’A NE FAKALOLOMA MOLE ‘A E FALALA’ANGA KOE FUA HONO MANAVA KITE ‘A PETELIHEMA SI’ONAU TUPU’ANGA \n\n 3. NE PAU KIA NAOMI KENE FOKI KI ‘ISILELI ‘O NE TALA KIA ‘O’OPA PEA MO LUTE KE NA FOKI KE NA FOKI KI MOAPE KI SI’ONA KAKAI NE FOKI ‘A ‘O’OPA KAE TANGI MUIMUI PE ‘A LUTE NAOMI ‘OUA TEKE O’I AU KEU LI’AKI KOE TEU MUIMUI KIATE KOE ‘O A’U KI HE MATE \n\n 4. KO HO KAKAI KO HOKU KAKAI PEA KO HO FONUA KO HOKU FONUA KO E POTU TE KE MATE AI ‘E TANU AI ‘A E SINO NI"),
    Book(
        number: "212",
        title: 'LE’O E ‘OKU KALANGA HE TOAFA',
        content:
            "1. LE’O E ‘OKU KALANGA ONGO MEI HE TOAFA KOE’UHI KE MOU TEUTEU ‘A E HALA TEU’I HO LOTO KE MA’A HE VAKAI KOE MISAIA HE KIKITE TALU MEIA ‘ATAMA \n\n TAU ANGELO ANGELO NA’A NE TALA NA’A NE TALA KOE ‘ALO KUO HIFO HE PO KO E TANGATA KO E TANGATA KO E ‘EIKI ‘O E MELINO KO SISU PE KO IA KOE TAUKAPO \n\n 2. FAKAHAKE MEI ‘ITENI KAE HIFO MAI ‘A SAILO PEA MO SIONE KO E FAKAMELOMELO FAKATAIPE HONO TALA KIKITE HE KAU POTO NA’A NAU ‘ATU ‘ A E MULA MO E LAIPENO"),
    Book(
        number: "213",
        title: 'FOKI MAI A HE KUO PO’ULI E',
        content:
            "1. FOKI MAI A HE KUO PO’ULI E (BASS) ‘OKU KEI TATALI MAI ‘A E TAMAI ‘OKU NE KE UIUI KIATE KOE MO AU ‘A E KAU MAFASIA FOKI MAI \n\n 2. LAHI TA’U ‘ENI MO SI’EKU HE MALO SISU HO’O ‘OFI MAI KUO KE FAKAHAOFI AU MEI HE MATE ‘OU ‘ILO PAU KO SISU ‘A E MO’UI \n\n 3. ‘OKU VAIVAI HOMAU LAUMALIE SISU KE TAU FE’AO PEA MO KOE KO E HALA FOU ‘I HE FAINGATA’A SISU TATAKI ‘A E FONONGA"),
    Book(
        number: "214",
        title: 'SISU E KE TA FE’AO PE',
        content:
            "1. HIKI E FONONGA SISU E TA FE’AO PE HE TOAFA FONU FAINGATA’A KAE FEFE TE U ‘ALU ‘O TALA E FEKAU (SOLO) NEONGO E AFA MOE PEAU SISU E KO AU ‘ENI FEKAU AU \n\n 2. HOKU ONGO NIMA ‘EIKI E KE TALI PE HA’O FOLOFOLA KEHE KE ‘AONGA KIATE KOE FOU HE MAMAHI MO E MATE SISU E TEU ‘ALU PE KEHE ‘A E MO’UI NI KE ‘AONGA PE \n\n 3. TEU FAKAFETA’I KI HOKU ‘EIKI MA’U PE KUO NE VETEANGE HOKU HA’ISIA MO’UI PE MALO FAU ‘E SISU E HO’O ‘OFA HULU KI HE ‘AUHE ‘O LAKAI ‘A E MO’UI NI MEI HE MATE \n\n 4. TEU FAKAMO’ONI KI HOKU ‘EIKI NE PEKIA FAI HE ONGO’I PEA MO E LOTO ‘APASIA KEHE KEU TU’U HE ‘AHO LAHI ‘O FAKAFE’AO KI HE TAMAI KO HOKU ‘’EIKI MO HOKU ‘OTUA LANGILANGI"),
    Book(
        number: "215",
        title: '‘OKU FAKA’OFO’OFA ‘A SAIONE',
        content:
            "1. ‘OKU FAKA’OFOFA ‘A SAIONE ‘I HE NGAUE ‘A E ‘EIKI PEA ULO ATU KI HE MAMANI ‘O TU’U TA’EUE’I TALA KI MAMANI HE FONUA KOTOA KE HA’U ‘O MA’U HOTAU TAPUAKI TAPUAKI \n\n 2. KIKITE’I ‘E HE KAU PALOFITA ‘E HOKO MAI ‘A E KUONGA ‘E MALANGA’AKI ‘A E FAKATOMALA MO E FAKAHAOHAOA TALA KI MAMANI HE FONUA KOTOA KE HA’U ‘O MA’U HOTAU TAPUAKI TAPUAKI \n\n 3. FOAKI ‘ENI ‘O NE MALANGA’I KI HE KAKAI PEA TUI HONGOFULU E ME’A KI HE ‘EIKI KAE MA’U ‘A E TOTONGI TALA KI MAMANI HE FONUA KOTOA KE HA’U ‘O MA’U HOTAU TAPUAKI TAPUAKI"),
    Book(
        number: "216",
        title: 'SISU KOE MAAMA',
        content:
            "1. SISU KO E MAAMA KI HOKU HALA KI HE FONONGA ‘I HE TOAFA NE U MEIMEI HUMU ‘IKAI HA U HE KO KALAISI KO E FAKAU \n\n 2. ‘A E TALAVOU MO E FINEMUI MOU ME’A MAI KE TAU ULUI TAU TUKUPA KI HE ‘EIKI HE KO KALAISI KO E FAKAU \n\n 3. FAKAFETA’I ‘A E ‘OFA HULU ‘OMI TUHULU KI HE MO’UI FAKAMALO AI PE MO HU HE KO KALAISI KO E FAKAU"),
    Book(
        number: "217",
        title: 'KO E FAKALELEI ‘O E 88',
        content:
            "1. KO E FAKALELEI ‘O E 88 KE TAU TALI MO FAKAPAPAU HOKO ‘A SISU KO E VUNIVALU KO E TAULAMA KIA KOE MO AU \n\n 2. HE NA’E KALUSEFAI ‘A SISU KO E FAKALELEI KIATE KOE MO AU HOKO ‘A E ANGAHALA ‘O TAAU KE NE NOFO HE TALONI ‘O E HAU \n\n TAU MOU HA’U A KE TAU HOLA ‘O UNGA KI HE TA’ATA’A NE HUA’I ‘A IA KO E VAI- VAI ‘O E MO’UI HE NA’E TAFE KO E HUHU’I \n\n 3. ‘OFA KE ONGO KI HE LOTO KOTOA ‘A SISU MO ‘ENE ‘OFA LI’OA HA’U A KE TA HOLA KIA SIHOVA KO E MALU’ANGA IA ‘O E FONONGA \n\n 4. TOKI ‘A HOKU MATA ‘O MAAMA KO E MO’UI ‘OKU TOE PE HANGA MOU TU’ULUTUI ‘O FAKATOMALA KO E TAIMI ‘OKU OFI NGATA"),
    Book(
        number: "218",
        title: '  KO HAI ‘OKU HA’U MO E KOFU KULOKULA',
        content:
            "1. KO HAI ‘ENA ‘OKU HA’U MO E KOFU KULOKULA (LAULALO) KO SISU ‘OKU LANU TA’ATA’A ‘OKU NE FUA ‘ETAU NGAAHI HIA SOLO (FASI, TENOA, OLOTO) \n\n 2. LAU NA’E FITU ‘A E FAKAMAAU’ANGA PEA TONU KI HE MATE (KI HE MATE) NAU SIPI’I IA (NAU SIPI’I IA) MO KAU’IMAEA (NAU ‘AI ‘A E ) ‘A E PALE TALATALA NA’A NE LANGA KO ENE ‘OFA (KO ‘ENE ‘OFA) \n\n 3. NA’A NAU HANGA ‘O TUTUKI (‘AKI ‘A E FA’O) ‘A HONO NIMA (MO HONO VA’E) NA’E HOKA’I (HONO VAKAVAKA) PUNA MEI AI ‘A E (TA’ATA’A) \n\n 4. SI’I TOTO (SI’I TOTO) NA’E TAFE (NA’E TAFE) MEI HONO (MEI HONO) SINO (SINO) KO E VAI (KO E VAI) FUFULU (‘A ‘ETAU HIA) \n\n SOLO TENOA) ‘E SIHOVA E FAKAMOLEMOLE A ‘A’AU HONO MAMAFA ‘A E FUA ‘EMAU HIA (‘A E FUA ‘EMAU HIA) (KATOA)"),
    Book(
        number: "219",
        title: '‘E AI E ‘AHO',
        content:
            "1. ‘E AI E ‘AHO TEU MAMATA TONU HOKU ‘EIKI ‘A E ‘AHO TE NE TAKI TONU ATU AU KI HE TAMAI FETAKINIMA FIEFIA TOKI ‘AHO FUNGANI TEU LATA AI KAU SIO PAU KI HOKU ‘EIKI \n\n 2. NEONGO PE HONO MASANI ‘O E NOFO KO ‘ENI KA ‘E MOLE VAVE PE ‘A HONO LANGILANGI TU’U LEVA LAKA ATU FAKA’AU KI ‘API HE ‘OKU VAVE PE ‘A ‘ENE HOKO MAI. \n\n 3. ‘A E ANGAHALA TAFOKI HE ‘OKU NE KEI UI TELIA NA’A HOKO MAI ‘A E ‘AHO LAHI TE KE HOPO MO E TU’I KO E HA HO’O TALI HE ‘OKU VAVE PE ‘A ‘ENE HOKO MAI"),
    Book(
        number: "220",
        title: '  SISU KOE MOONI MO E HALA (SIONE 14:6)',
        content:
            "1. SISU KO E MO’ONI MOE HALA TAKI TONU KI HE MO’UI TA’ENGATA KO KOE PE ‘A E ‘ALUNGA PEA ‘IKAI HA TOE FOUNGA \n\n 2. AFIO MAI KI HE’EMAU LOTU TANGI PE MO UI ATU SISU ALA MAI MU’A HO’O TO’OKUPU HIKI HAKE AU MEI HE VANU \n\n 3. KO KOE HOKU ‘AMANAKI’ANGA KO KOE HOKU ‘OFA ‘OFA’ANGA FOTU MAI HO’O FOFONGA ‘OFA KO HAI IA TE NE FAKATATAUA"),
    Book(
        number: "221",
        title: 'LAHI ‘EIKI ‘EKU HOHA’A',
        content:
            "1. LAHI ‘EIKI ‘EKU HOHA’A KI HE KOLOA ‘O MAMANI MALU’I ‘EKU FAKAKAUKAU KEKE TATAKI MO TOFA HALA ‘OKU OU MASIVA ‘I HO’O FOLOFOLA \n\n 2. TOKONI ‘EIKI KEU FIE LAU PEA KE AKO MO FUFU KEU FANONGO MO LAU LOTOA TALANGOFUA MO TAUHI MA’U ‘I HE ‘AHO PEA MOE PO HO’O FOLOFOLA"),
    Book(
        number: "222",
        title: 'NE PALOFISAI ‘A SOLOMONE',
        content:
            "1. NE PALOFISAI E SOLOMONE ‘E HA’U KO E TAUHI LELEI ‘O E FANGA SIPI HE NA’A NE HIFO MAI ‘I HE’ENE ‘OFA LAHI NA’A NE ‘ILO PE KUO PAU KE PEKIA NE TANGI MAMAHI HE MGOUE KO KETISEMANI TUKU KIA AU KEU TAU MOE MAMAHI ‘I HE HIA ‘A MAMANI. \n\n 2. SISU KOE TAUHI LELEI ‘O E FALE ‘O ‘ISILELI NA’A NE KUMI HE ‘AHO MOE PO KO E LE’O E ‘OKU ONGO MAI ‘I HE LONGONOA ‘AE PO KO E LE’O IA ‘O E MAMAHI KO AU PE KO E HALA KI HE MO’UI TA’ENGATA HA’U PE ‘A KO E ‘OKU FIE MO’UI. \n\n 3. NGUNGU ……………….. \n\n Trio KO FUTU EKU UI, TANGI MO TUKITUKI TO’O ‘A E MATAPA KIA AU TO’O ATU KE TA FE’AO MO AU KUO VIKU HOKU ‘ULU ‘I HE HAHAU ‘O E PO NA’E ALA HE MATAPA, ‘ALAHA MAI ‘A E MULA AFE NAI TEKE UI KUO PONGIA AU HE’EKU ‘OFA \n\n 4. KOE LE’O E ‘OKU ONGO MAI KOE LE’O IA ‘O E TANGI KOE LE’O IA ‘OE MAMAHI HE’ENE ‘ILO ‘ENE SIPI HE ‘OKU MOHE MA’U TANGI MO UI 2 TANGI MO UI ‘I HE MATAPA HE KUO LONGONOA ‘A E PO LONGONOA ‘A E PO"),
    Book(
        number: "223",
        title: '‘E ‘EIKI FOAKI MAI',
        content:
            "1. ‘E EIKI FOAKI MAI KI HOKU LAUMALIE NI ‘A E NONGA ‘A HO’O KELESI KEU MA’U ‘A E MA’ONI’ONI \n\n 2. KO AU ‘ENI KO E ANGAHALA TEU HU ATU KI HE AFIO NA MALO HO’O MAU KOLOA KI HE SINO, ATAMAI KOTOA \n\n 3. TEU FIEFIA ‘AHO MO E PO KEU FEINGA KE FAI HO FINANGALO TOKONI’I ‘A HOKU LOTO KE ‘OUA NA’A KU TOE MAMA’O \n\n TAU ‘EIKI E TOKONI MAI ‘EIKI E TOKONI MAI MALU’I AU MEI HE FILI KEU HU ‘O NOFO ‘ITANITI"),
    Book(
        number: "224",
        title: 'HE NA’E PEHE ‘A E ‘OFA MAI',
        content:
            "1. HE NA’E PEHE ‘A E ‘OFA MAI ‘A HOTAU ‘OTUA NE FOAKI HONO ‘ALO TOFU PE TAHA KO IA ‘E TUI KIATE IA ‘E IKAI TE NE ‘AUHA KA E MA’U ‘A E MO’UI TA’ENGATA \n\n 2. KO HAI E LAU ‘A E FIEFIA MO E NONGA KUO TE MA’U TALU HOKU FAKATAU’ATAINA MEI HE MATE MO E A’USIA HULU ‘A ‘EKU HIA HE TA’ATA’A TAPU ‘O E ‘OTUA \n\n 3. ‘E ‘IKAI PE TEU TUKUHAUSIA SISU PE ‘A HOKU TAKAUA KO E SIPI AU IA NEONGO NEU SI’I HE SISU E KETA FE’AO MA’U PE \n\n 4. FOAKI HO TALENITI PEA HANGE HA MATEAKI FA’A KATAKI HE FUA KOLOSI TAFESINO’I VAI HE NGAUE ‘A E ‘EIKI HE NA’E PEKIA KO HOTAU FETONGI \n\n 5. ‘E ‘IKAI LI’AKI AU ‘OFA ‘A KALAISI HE’IKAI TE NE LIAKI AU ‘OKU OU ‘ILO’I HA POTU PE TEU ‘ALU AI HE’IKAI TENE LIAKI AU"),
    Book(
        number: "225",
        title: '‘E ‘OTUA FUNGANI MA’OLUNGA',
        content:
            "1. ‘E ‘OTUA FUNGANI MA’OLUNGA ‘ALO’OFA MAI KOE MASIVA AU ‘EIKI E \n\n 2. TUKU PE ‘IATE KOE HOKU LAUMALIE VAIAVAI MA’U PE ‘E TAMAI FONU ‘I HE ‘ALO’OFA ‘O TA’ENGATA \n\n 3. NEU TO’O PE ‘EKU HIA ‘O ‘ATU KI HO NIMA MAFIMAFI KO E HIA AU MO E MASIVA ‘E TAMAI E KEU ‘IATE KOE \n\n 4. HU’I A ‘ETA HA’AMONGA APASIA KI HE ‘OTUA KA TAU MA’U ‘A E MO’UI ‘O TA’ENGATA ‘OKA HILI ‘A E NUNU MOVETE NI KEU ‘IA TE KOE SISU E KO KOE PE KOE FAKALALOA MO E FAKAMO’UI"),
    Book(
        number: "226",
        title: '‘E ‘OTUA KO E TAMAI',
        content:
            "1. ‘E ‘OTUA KO E TAMAI TEU HU ATU HE ‘AHO NI PEA MO E LOTO FAKAFETA’I KI HE LELEI KUO MAU MO’UI AI KO E FETU’U ‘I LANGI E KOLOA HE FUNGA ‘O E FONUA ‘A E NAUNAU HO NIMA E KUO FAKAHA ‘E NATULA \n\n 2. KO E ‘OFA KUO LI’OA TUKU HO ‘ALO KE PEKIA KO IA ‘A E MO’UI’ANGA KI HA TAHA KUO NE TALI IA KALEVALE MO E KOLOSI PEKIA’ANGA HOTAU ‘EIKI KUO LAVA PEA KUO ‘OSI MA’U A MU’A ‘A E MO’UI \n\n TAU TEU HIVA FAKAFETA’I KI HOKU ‘EIKI KI HE’ENE ‘OFA, KI HE’ENE ‘OFA TEU HIVA FAKAFETA’I KI HOKU ‘EIKI KI HE’ENE ‘OFA ‘OFA HE ANGAHALA"),
    Book(
        number: "227",
        title: '‘E LAU ‘E HAI SI’A ‘OFA PEHE',
        content:
            "1. ‘E LAU ‘E HAI SI’A ‘OFA PEHE ‘ENE FOAKI ‘ENE MO’UI KE MOLE KO E MAKA FUNGANI KOE NE SILA’I PEA LI’AKI KE MOLE \n\n 2. TOKI ‘OFA KA FUNGANI HAKE ‘OI ‘A E ‘OFA NE ‘IKAI MAMAE NE FOAKI MA’AU HA MO’UI ‘O KAPAU TEKE LOTO KE TUI \n\n 3. ‘E TAMAI ‘OUA MU’A E LAU LAU PE MU’A ‘ENE HIA MA’AKU NEONGO PE KO E HA HONO LAHI KEHE PE KE NE FOKI MAI \n\n TAU TEKE LI’AKI NAI ‘A SISU TEKE SI’AKI HO MONUU ‘ALU MU’A KO E KI AI TENE KEI TALI MAI"),
    Book(
        number: "228",
        title: '‘E SISU ‘OKU OU VAKAI',
        content:
            "1. ‘E SISU ‘OKU OU VAKAI HO’O ‘OFA PEHE FAU HO TAUTAU KOVI HE ‘AKAU ‘O MATE PE MA’AKU \n\n 2. ‘A E ANGAHALA LOTU MO KE FAKAKAUKAU MU’A KI HE FU’U ‘OFA LAHI KO IA NE MA’A AI ‘ETAU HIA \n\n 3. KO E MONU’IA HA TAHA ‘E TALI ‘A E TUKITUKI KAI ‘OHOMOHE MO E ‘EIKI PEA TOE HU KI AI \n\n TAU FIE FANONGO MU’A KI HE UI SISU ‘ENA ‘OKU TUKITUKI FAKAAVA HOTAU LOTO KA E HU MAI KE TAU NONOFO"),
    Book(
        number: "229",
        title: '‘OIAU HE UI ‘A SISU MEI LANGI',
        content:
            "1. ‘OIAU HE UI ‘A SISU MEI LANGI UI KIA KO E MO AU VAKAI KI ‘OLUNGA HE TA’ALO MAI UI KIA KO E MO AU \n\n 2. KO HAI TENE LAU ‘A E ‘OFA ‘OFA KIA KOE MO AU NEONGO ‘A E KOVI NA’A TE FEIA ‘OFA KIA KOE MO AU \n\n 3. ‘E TOE TA’ALO KE ‘UMA’AKI KO SISU ‘OKU TA’ALO MAI ‘E TOE TEKE’I KOE ‘UMA’AKI KAU ONGOSIA HU MAI \n\n TAU HU MAI HU MAI KAU ONGOSIA HU MAI TA’ALO MO UI ‘A SISU MEI LANGI KAU MAFASIA HU MAI"),
    Book(
        number: "230",
        title: '‘EIKI TOKONI MAI MU’A',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI TOKONI MAI MU’A FAKA’A HOMAU MATA KO ‘ENI E ‘AHO MO E KUONGA FAKATOKANGA HO FOLOFOLA HANGE NA’E HOKO HE ‘AHO ‘O NOA ‘E PEHE PE ‘A E NGATA’ANGA NAU KAI MO INU HE ‘AHO KOTOA TULIA E MAMANI MO HONO MALIE \n\n 2. PEHE PE KO E ‘ATUNGA LAU ‘A E HA HA TUKU AI HO FAKAMAAU KAPAU E LEA MAI ‘A FA’ITOKA ‘OKU OU ‘ILO’IA MAI HOMOU MONU’IA MOU MA’U ‘A E TAIMI MO E HOUA KE MOU TAFOKI ‘O HANGA HAKE A KE LEA MO E FOHA MAUMAU KOLOA ‘APA TAMAI KUOU FAIANGAHALA \n\n TAU ‘EIKI FAKAMOLEMOLE MAUTOLU ‘ENI KUO MAU HE TE MAU TOE ‘ALU NAI KI FE KO E MO’UI NI ‘OKU ‘IATE KOE PE"),
    Book(
        number: "231",
        title: 'EIKI SISU E',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI SISU E, ‘E ‘EIKI E KO HAI MO AU KE MA FE’AO SISU E KO KOE PE NEU HAO AI \n\n 2. ‘OKU KE ‘AFIO’I ‘A E LAHI ‘O E FAINGATA’A HE FONONGA’ANGA SISU E ALA MAI HO NIMA ‘OFA \n\n 3. OFE’I MAI ‘EIKI SI’O FOFONGA KI HE LE’O ‘O ‘EKU KALANGA HE KUO OFI MAI ‘A FA’ITOKA \n\n TAU KO E HIKI ‘ENI ‘A E FONONGA KE LAKA ATU HE TOAFA SISU E TAKIMU’A FAINGOFUA FAINGATA’A KUOU HAO FAKAMALU ‘I HE’ETAU FONONGA"),
    Book(
        number: "232",
        title: '‘EIKI SISU KE KE FOFONGA HIFO',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI SISU E KEKE FOFONGA HIFO ‘EKU FEILAULAU KE FAKAKAKATO KUOU FOAKI AU MOE ME’A KUOU ‘ILO’I KEHE KEU MA’A ‘I HO’O AFIO \n\n 2. ‘E ‘EIKI SISU ‘OKU OU TATALI ‘I HO’O VE’E VA’E NA’E TUTUKI KO E TA’ATA’A NA’E TAFE AI KO E VAI FUFULU IA TEU MA’A AI \n\n 3. ‘OKU OU TATALI ATU ‘E SISU FAKATUPU ‘IA AU HA LOTO FO’OU KO KINAUTOLU TE NAU KUMI ATU KE KE FAKAFO’OU MO KINAUTOLU \n\n 4. ‘EIKI KO HOKU LOTO KEU HAOHAOA PEA KE ‘AFIO AI ‘A E ‘AFIONA HOLOKI KI LALO ‘A E HOLI KOTOA FUFULU AU PEA TEU HINEHINA"),
    Book(
        number: "233",
        title: '‘EIKI TEU NOFO PE ‘O HIVA',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI TEU NOFO PE ‘O HIVA FAKAFETA’I HO’O FAKAKOLOA ‘ETE TAKI ‘A KALAISI MO E FAKA’ILONGAUA NEONGO NE KEI TA’EMAHINO KAE FAKAFETA’I KUOU A’USIA ‘I HE KELESI KUO NE FOAKI TONUNGA FAKAMO’ONI ‘OKU MO’UI ‘A HOKU ‘OTUA \n\n 2. LAHI ‘A E FILI MO E ‘AHI’AHI KA NA’E LAVA PE KE MATATALI FIHITU’U ‘A E FAINGATA’A MO E PALOPALEMA KA NA’E LAVA PE HONO FAKANONGA NA’E TAHA PE HONO ‘UHINGA FETONGI AU ‘E KALAISI TU’UNGA’A \n\n TAU FAKAFETA’I SISU, FAKAFETA’I ‘EIKI ‘I HE’EKU MA’U KOE KO HOKU FAKAMO’UI NONGA, FIEMALIE, FIEFIA TAU’ATAINA, ‘OFA PEA MOE TUI FIEFIA PE ‘EIKI KUOU MO’UI"),
    Book(
        number: "234",
        title: 'KUO UNGA AU KI HE NGOUE VAINE',
        content:
