        title: 'MALO MU’A SISU SI’O ‘OFA ‘AUFUATO',
        content:
            "1. MALO MU’A SISU SI’O ‘OFA ‘AUFUATO LAVE AI AU KO E ANGAHALA MO’UI MALO ‘ISA ‘ETE FAKAPO’ULI TA’E HOUNGA KI HOKU LOTO HO’O PEKIA ‘IKAI HALAIA KE FAI HOKU TAUKAPO \n\n 2. ‘OIAUE ‘E ‘IKAI HE’IKAI TEA FA’A LAVA MANATU KI HE KUOHILI MOE FOLAU ‘IKAI HA TAULANGA TONU KEU ‘AUHIA PE LOMEKINA ‘I HE FAKAEVAHA TEU TANGI MO UI ‘EIKI E TA ‘OKU KE ‘I VAKA \n\n TAU ‘ATONAI E TUKU KE HOUNGA KI HOKU LOTO ‘A HO’O TULUTA TOTO MO E UHU ‘A E MATA ‘O E TAO ‘IKAI TE KE ‘EKEA HA TOTONGI KI HO MATAKAFO NGAOHI A ‘EKU MO’UI KE TAAU MO HO’O MANAKO \n\n 3. FAKAMOLEMOLE’I AU MO SI’EKU FAKAFEANGAI ‘A E TO NOUNOU MO E KINOHA’A ‘O E MO’UI TEU LEA FAKATAHA MO E FOHA NE FOKI KI ‘AI KUOU ANGAHALA KI HE LANGI KAE TAU TONU KI HE TAMAI \n\n 4. ‘EIKI KE KE FAKANAVAU ‘A SI’OKU LAUMALIE KE ‘OUA NA’A KU TOE ANGAHALA KIATE KOE ‘OMI HA KONISENISI HANGE KO E LAU ‘A E PUNAKE HANGE HA TAMA’IMATA KEU KALO MEIA SETANE"),
    Book(
        number: "261",
        title: 'KO E MO’UI NI NE PAU KE MOLE',
        content:
            "1. KO E MO’UI NI NE PAU KE MATE HANGE HA VAKA KUO ‘ULI MO TAFOE HANGE KO PATIMIOSI SI’EKU KOLE ‘ALO’OFA MAI SISU KEU ‘A PE \n\n 2. NEONGO NE HANGE KUOTE LI’EKINA ‘IKAI HA FALALA’ANGA KE TAUHIA KO E ‘OTUA PE HOKU HUFANGA’ANGA HOKU PALETU’A ‘I HE FAINGATA’A \n\n TAU HOKU FOUNGA KUOU TUKU KI LANGI HE’IKAI HA ME’A ‘E FEHALAAKI ‘AOTEAROA E KE TALIA MAI KEU HOKO PE KO HO TAPUAKI \n\n 3. ‘OKATOPA ‘AHO 14 ‘O E 98 FEKAMAAKI E LOTO ‘I HE VAHAFOLAU TANGI MO E TO’E ‘EIKI FAKAMO’UI AU ‘EKU KAPASA PE KO E TOHITAPU \n\n 4. MALO SISU E LAHI HO’O ‘OFA ‘E ‘IKAI TEKE TUKU KEU TUENOA NEONGO ‘A E FELE ‘O E PALOPALEMA KO E ‘OTUA PE KOE VAI FAKANONGA"),
    Book(
        number: "262",
        title: 'TEU TALANOA KI HONO FAKAOFO',
        content:
            "1. TEU TALANOA KI HONO FAKAOFO ‘AHO NEKE ALAMAI KI HOKU LOTO ‘EIKI HE’IKAI LAVA KEKE NGALO HE KOE MO’UI NI IA KUOU TUKULOLO \n\n 2. NEU FOLAU MAI KI HE FONUA NI KO E AMANAKI KI HONO MASANI KA KOE KONGA HO’O PALANI KEU FE’ILOAKI AI MO HOKU HUHU’I \n\n TAU TEU HIVA MOU ME’E KIATE KOE ‘O FAKAHIKIHIKI HO HUAFA PE LAU TA’U ‘EKU HEHENOA PE KA KUO KE HULUNGIA HOKU LAUMALIE \n\n 3. TEU LEA FAKATAHA MO HO’O FOLOFOLA KA TOKI ‘IA KALAISI HA TOKO TAHA PEA MOLE ATU ‘A E ANGA MOTU’A KAE HOKO ‘O FO’OU ‘A E ME’A KOTOA \n\n 4. KO E FAKA’ANUA IA HOKU LOTO KEU FAI PE MU’A HO FINANGALO ‘OMI ‘A E POTO PEA MOE ‘ILO KEU FAI HO’O NGAUE MEI HOKU LOTO"),
    Book(
        number: "263",
        title: 'TEU HANGA HAKE A KI HE MO’UNGA',
        content:
            "1. TEU HANGA HAKE A KI HE MO’UNGA HOKU TOKONI MEIA SIHOVA NA’A NE NGOHI ‘A E LANGI MO E FONUA KO IA KOE ‘ALIFA MO E ‘OMEKA \n\n 2. KO E ‘OTUA KO E HUFANGA MO E MALOHI KO E TOKONI OFI ‘I HE MAMAHI ‘E ‘IKAI TEU MANAVAHE KI MAMANI PE HIKI ‘A E MO’UNGA KI LOTO LANGI \n\n TAU HE’IKAI KE TUKIA HO VA’E ‘OKU NE TAUHI ‘O ‘IKAI TULEMOHE ‘OKU NE FAKAHAOFI KOE MEI HE KOVI KOTOA PE KE FAKAMO’ONI ‘A E SAAAME \n\n 3. KA ‘IKAI KAU IA HE LANGA HO FALE KO E KULANOA HO’O NGAUE ‘IKAI ‘AONGA E TU’U HENGIHENGI PE ‘OKU NE FAKAMOHE ‘A ‘ENE PELE \n\n 4. KAPAU ‘E ‘IKAI TAUHI ‘E IA ‘A E KOLO KO E KULANOA ‘A E KAU LE’O KAE MONU’IA ‘A E FAKAMELINO ‘OKU NE NGAUE MEI HONO LOTO"),
    Book(
        number: "264",
        title: '‘EIKI KO KOE PE ‘A HOKU MALOHI',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI KO KOE PE ‘A HOKU MALOHI TEU HOLA KIA HAI KO KOE PE TUKU KEU MO’UI PE HO’O KELESI HAO’ANGA HOKU LAUMALIE \n\n 2. KO ‘EKU MO’UI NI KUO LUVA KAKATO KEU HOKO PE KO E SEVANITI TALANGOFUA FAI HO FINANGALO ‘I HENI PEA MO ‘ITANITI \n\n TAU PUKE NIMA AU SISU KETA FE’AO HE KO E FONONGA NI ‘OKU FUOLOA FAU ‘EIKI MALO MU’A ‘A E TAULAMA HAO KUOU MALU ‘I HO KAPAKAU \n\n 3. KA ‘I AI LEVA HA FEHALAAKI KOU ‘AMANAKI TEKE ‘ALO’OFA ‘OMI KE FAI HA TOE HELIAKI KEHE KEU MATA SI’O FOFONGA \n\n 4. KO E LAU E IA HO’O FOLOFOLA KO E TALANGOFUA ‘E TAPUAKI FAI ‘ENE NGAUE ‘AKI HO KOTOA KE FAKAFOTUNGA HONO ‘IMISI"),
    Book(
        number: "265",
        title: 'KO HAI NAI ‘OKU FIEFIA (SAKEASI)',
        content:
            "TAU KO HAI NAI ‘OKU FIEFIA KO HAI NAI ‘OKU TENGIHIA KUO ‘OSI FAI HOTA FAKALALOA KO E LAMI ‘AVE IA KUO NE ‘OSI PEKIA \n\n 1. FANONGO MAI KAU TALAATU A ‘A E LAU ‘A E TOHITAPU KOE MATE TA TU’OTAHA HILI IA KO E FAKAMAAU PEA ‘E ‘ALU KI HE LELEI ‘A E KAU ANGATONU KAE IKU KI HE MAMAHI ‘A E KAU TA’ELOTU \n\n 2. TAU FANONGO PEA VAKAI KI HE TANGATA KO NIKOTIMASI KO E TAKI ‘O E SIASI PEA FUA KAVENGA LALAHI NEONGO KOTOA ‘A E NGAAHI ME’A NI MAHINO PE ‘ENE TA’EPAASI FANAU’I FO’OU, FAKATOMALA TOKI LAVA HAKE KI LANGI \n\n 3. KO SAKEASI KO E TANGATA PUKUPUKU MO KOLOA’IA TANAKI TUKUHAU KAKA FEHI’ANEKINA NE FAIFAI ‘ONE A’U MAI KI HE FU’U SUKAMINO ‘ONE KAKA KI ‘OLUNGA FAI MEI AI E FAKASIO \n\n 4. NE ‘IKAI KE FUOLOA MO E HA’ELE MAI ‘E ‘ALO ‘ONE MEA’I ‘A SAKEASI MO E ANGA SI’ENE NOFO ‘ONE PEHE KO E KALASI ‘ENI ‘OKU TONU KE ‘ILO FOLOFOLA HAKE SAKEASI HIFO KI LALO NA’A KE TO \n\n 5. LAULAU TO’A MO E MALOHI TAU PETI PE ‘IA SAMISONI KA LOLOA HONO ‘A ‘ULU MAHINO PE HE’IKAI TOE FO’I KA KO E PANGO HE KOE HOA NA’E ‘IKAI KE ‘OFA MO’ONI NE IKU PE ‘ONE MATE AI KO E FUA ‘ENE FILI MALI KOVI \n\n 6. TAHA E TA NE FAKAMAMAHI PEA ‘OKU KEI HOKO MAI SALOME MO HELOTIASI MO ‘ENA TA’E’OFA NA’E FAI TUVA E KOLOA ‘A HELOTA KA NA’E ‘IKAI KE NA NONGA AI TA KO E ME’A MASILA ‘OKU TAPU PE KE ‘AKAHI"),
    Book(
        number: "266",
        title: 'NEU FOU ATU HE ‘AHO ‘E TAHA',
        content:
            "1. NEU FOU ATU HE ‘AHO ‘E TAHA KI HE ‘API ‘O E KAU PAEA NEU TU’U SI’I HIFO HALA ‘O VAKAI SI’ENAU VA’INGA UMIUMI NOA PE SI’A TAMA ‘OU ‘EKEANGE HONO ‘UHINGA TA KO E KUI ‘IKAI LAVA KE ‘A TAFOKI ‘ONE TANGI LEVA \n\n 2. KO E KAKAI ‘OKU NAU HA’U KO E ‘AVE SI’ANAU FANAU PAU PE ‘OKU NAU FIEMA’U ‘EKU TUKUHAUSIA KE FEAU TU’AMELIE KETE KAU ‘I HE LAU KA KOE’UHI KO E KUI AU TAHA KEHE MA’U PE ‘AVE NAUTOLU KAE SI’I LIAKI PE AU \n\n TAU KO AU KO E LI’EKINA KO AU KO E LI’EKINA MATALA’I ’AKAU ‘ATA ‘OKU TU’U HE POTU LALA ‘O ‘IKAI HA FA’E KE ‘UMA PE HA TAMAI KE KATAKATA ‘O IKAI PE HA TOE TAHA KO AU KO E LI’EKINA \n\n 3. HALA HA FA’E KE ALA MAI ‘O AMOHI AU ‘O KAU KA TANGI ONGO’I TA’ELATA HE TAIMI NI’IHI IFO ‘A E MATE ‘I HE MO’UI KEU FOU ‘I HE HALA KI HEVANI LAVA SIO KOTOA ‘OUA ‘E KUI PEAU TATAU AI MO E TAMAIKI ‘O MA’U SI’OKU ‘API"),
    Book(
        number: "267",
        title: '‘EIKI KEKE TATAKI ‘A E PILIKIMI NI',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI KEKE TATAKI ‘A E PILIKIMI NI KE MAU LELE ‘I MATANGI FANONGO KI HE’EMAU HIVA MO E TANGI ‘EIKI E TA FONONGA KI ‘API \n\n 2. ‘EIKI PUKENIMA AU ‘I HE’EKU FOLAU MO’UI NI MO HONO PEAU MAHU’INGA TAHA PE ‘A KOE SISU ‘EIKI E TA FONONGA KE A’U"),
    Book(
        number: "268",
        title: '‘EIKI SIHOVA KO E ‘OTUA (HIMI 363)',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI SIHOVA KO E ‘OTUA NA’A KE ‘AFIO TALU MEI MU’A TAUPOTU KOE SI’I TAHA AU KAKE MANATU SI’O FANAU \n\n 2. HE KOHO ‘ALO KUOU LAVA’I HOKU HUHU’I KEU HAO AI ‘OUA E HOUHAU ‘OUA ‘E TAUTEA KAKE MANATU HONO LAVEA \n\n 3. PEA KE HIFO KIATE AU HO LAUMALIE KE NOFO MA’U KENE HUFAKI MO NE TOKONI MONE TATAKI KI HE MO’ONI \n\n TAU ‘EIKI TAUPOTU KO E TAMAI TALI ‘A E LOTU ‘OKU OU FAI"),
    Book(
        number: "269",
        title: 'ANGA ‘ETAU MO’UI',
        content:
            "1. ANGA ‘ETAU MO’UI TAKITAHA FAI ‘ENE FILI HALA HOKU MATA MATATOTONU KI HE’ETAU FAKAKAUKAU TAUMAIA ‘OKU TUKU AI ‘A E ‘OFA MAI ‘A E TAMAI FOLOFOLA MAI PE , TAU ‘ALU ANGE HE KO IA PE FIEMALIE \n\n 2. KAPAU TE TAU KI’I NOFO HIFO TAU FAKALAULAULOTO SIO ATU KI HE KUOHILI VAA’IHALA TAU FOU MAI AI ME’A E TE TAU ‘ILO’I KUO LAHI FAU ‘ENE KELESI HA NAI ‘OKU TAU KEI TATALI AI TA KKO E ‘AHO ‘ENI HOTO FAKAMO’UI \n\n TAU MALO SISU HO’O KEI FIEMA’U MAUTOLU NEONGO TA’ETAAU KAINGA E TAU MONU’IA TAU TALI A MU’A ‘ENE ‘OFA."),
    Book(
        number: "270",
        title: 'AKO’I SISU ‘A HOKU LOTO (‘EVANGELIO)',
        content:
            "1. AKO’I SISU ‘A HOKU LOTO KEU ‘ILO HO FINANGALO KEU TALA HO ONGOONGO ‘I HE ‘AHO PEA MO E PO KO E NGAUE ‘EVANGELIO \n\n 2. KO E HOKO MAI ‘A E ‘ALO KO E ‘OMI E FAKAMO’UI KO E KOLOA FUNGANI KE TUFAKI TALAVOU, FINEMUI KE TALI KE KUMUNI IA KE MASANI \n\n 3. SISU TOE UI PE AU ‘O HANGE KO HO’O FEKAU HEI’ILO PE TEU TAAU ‘O HOA MO HO’O FEKAU KEU TALA ‘A E ONGOONGO KE A’U \n\n TAU SISU E, SISU E, SISU E KO AU ‘ENI, KO AU ‘ENI, KO AU ‘ENI TEU LOTO KEU ‘ALU HE ‘OKU KE ‘IATE AU"),
    Book(
        number: "271",
        title: 'FAKAPO’ULI ‘O E ANGAHALA',
        content:
            "1. FAKAPO’ULI ‘A E ANGAHALA KAFO MO’ONI AI ‘A HOKU LOTO FAKATOMALA MO ‘EKU LOTU ‘IA SISU TOKONI’I AU \n\n 2. NE FU’U ONGOSIA ‘EKU MO’UI FEINGA KE FAKAHAOFI HA SIPI KAPAU ‘E ‘IKAI ‘A SISU MO AU ‘E ‘IKAI TEU IKUNA’I \n\n 3. ‘IKAI FA’A LAU ‘A ‘EKU KOVI TONU KE MOLE ‘A ‘EKU MO’UI NEKE KUMI AU KE FAKAMO’UI ‘IA SISU KO HOKU HUHU’I \n\n 4. SISU NE ‘OFA KIA AU"),
    Book(
        number: "272",
        title: 'FALALA KI HE ‘OTUA',
        content:
            "1. FALALA KI HE ‘OTUA KO IA PE ‘A E HAO’ANGA NEONGO ‘A E FAINGATA’A KO SISU PE TENE LAVA HIVA, HIVA HE KEI ‘AHO HIVA, HIVA AI PE HE PO MA’U AI PE, MA’U AI PE KE TAU HIVA, HIVA, HIVA \n\n 2. TRUST IN THE LORD AND DON’T GIVE UP HE IS A SO TRUE TO YOU NO MATTER WHAT YOUR TROUBLES ARE JESUES WILL SEE THROUGH SING, SING WHILE THE DAY IS BRIGHT SING, SING WHILE THE NIGHT IS DARK SING, SING, SING"),
    Book(
        number: "273",
        title: 'FIHA NAI TA’U E MO SI’ETE KEI PULE',
        content:
            "1. FIHA NAI TA’U E MO SI’ETE KEI PULE SISU KI HOKU LAUMALIE TA KO ‘ENI PE ‘A HOKU FAINGAMALIE KEU TALI KOE ‘O A’U KI HA’AKU MATE \n\n 2. LAHI FAU ‘A E TAIMI PULE ‘A E FILI HE MO’UI ‘EIKI KA NA’A KE KEI UI ‘I HE ‘AHO PEA MO E PO KA NA’E ONGO KI HOKU LOTO ‘OFA NE ‘AU KI HE FONUALOTO \n\n TAU SISU PULE ‘IATE AU HOKU LAUMALIE KE MA’U KEU HOKO KO HO’O TALAFEKAU TOKONI’I ‘EKU MO’UI KE HA AI PE HO ‘IMISI PEA KE ‘EIKI KOE ‘I HE’EKU MO’UI"),
    Book(
        number: "274",
        title: 'KO KITAUA E KO E FIKI TA’EFUA',
        content:
            "1. KO KITAUA E KO E FIKI TA’EFUA NE FAI KI AI ‘A E FOLOFOLA ‘A E ‘OTUA KA KO ‘ENI HOTA FAINGAMALIE ‘ETA MA’U HA TAUHI ‘OFA PEHE \n\n 2. ‘I HE HA’ELE ATU ‘A E ‘EIKI KO E KUMI FUA HE’ENE NGOUE ‘ONE VAKAI ‘OKU ‘IKAI FUA ‘O NE LOTO LEVA KENE TA’AKI \n\n 3. PEA KOLEANGE ‘E HE TAUHI TUKU AI PE ‘I HE TA’U NI KAE’OUA KEU KELI TAKAI MO TAUFETUKU KI AI \n\n TAU MALO SISU HO’O ‘OFA HO’O ‘IKAI TEKE TUKU KE TA KA KE TOE HUFEKINA ‘A E FIKI TA’EFUA"),
    Book(
        number: "275",
        title: '‘E FAI HA FOAKI PALE ‘I HE LANGI',
        content:
            "1. ‘E FAI HA FOAKI PALE ‘I HE LANGI KALAUNI E FOAKI MAI ‘E HE TAMAI HE KO E ‘AHO ‘O E MAVAVA PEA KO E ‘AHO IA ‘O E FIEFIA LAHI \n\n 2. TEU TA’ATA’ALO ATU PEA KE TA’ATA’ALO MAI TEU MALIMALI ATU PEA KE MALIMALI MAI TETA PUKENIMA AI FIEFIA MO FAKAHAA’I ‘I HE TALONI ‘O E LAMI \n\n 3. HOTA TEUNGA TE TA TUI ‘OKU LANGILANGI’IA HINAPAKI PEA ‘ASINISINI HANGE HA SAFAILA NOFO’ANGA KO E KOLO FONU MAKA MAHU’INGA KO E KOULA HAOHAOA \n\n TAU TETA HU ‘I HONO MATAPA FAKAKAKATO ‘ENE TALA’OFA ‘EVE’EVA ‘I HONO HALA KOULA FEOHI PEA MO E ‘OTUA KO E SELAFIMI ‘E ‘I AI KETA KAUNGA FAKAFETA’I TAU HU KI HE NOFO’A MASANI KO E FIEFIA PE ‘I AI"),
    Book(
        number: "276",
        title: 'KUO LAHI FAU ‘A E TAIMI ( Foha maumau)',
        content:
            "1. KUO LAHI FAU ‘A E TAIMI NEU LI’AKI AI KOE ‘EIKI E KA NA’AKE KEI TULIMUI MAI PE ‘IKAI TEKE LAU ‘A ‘EKU VALE MO ‘EKU MATE KA KUO KE LOTO KE UI AU KO HO’O PELE \n\n 2. KO AU ‘A E FOHA NEU MAUMAU’I ‘A E KOLOA ‘OU LOTO KEU MAVAHE MEI HE ‘AFIONA KA NA’E KEI TULIMUI MAI PE HO’O ‘OFA ‘O KE TOE LOTO PE KE UI KO HO FOHA \n\n 3. SISU MALO MU’A HO’O ‘OFA PEHE FAU LAVE AI ‘A E HIAMATEA KO AU KO AU ‘ENI KOU HU ATU MO PUNOU ‘EIKI ‘ALO’OFA MU’A ‘ATU A AU MA’AU \n\n TAU KA NEONGO PE ‘OKU LANU FEFE ‘A HO’O NGAAHI ANGAHALA ‘E LAVA NOA PE HO FAKAMOLEMOLE SISU ‘ENA KEI TALI PE (SISU PE)"),
    Book(
        number: "277",
        title: 'TAMA TUKU MU’A HO’O FA’A PEHE',
        content:
            "1. TAMA TUKU A MU’A HO’O FA’A PEHE LAHI PE FAINGAMALIE NA’A FAIFAI PEA KE IKU ‘O HANGE KAU TAUPO’OU VALE HOKOSIA E TAIMI ‘E PA AI E TALUPITE NAU TOKI ‘OHOVALE HE’ENAU ‘ILO KUO ‘IKAI HA’A NAU LOLO PANGO HE KUO TU’UAPO \n\n 2. HE’IKAI TEU MA KE FAKAMATALA FIEFIA KUOU A’USIA TAIMI ‘OKA HOKO ‘AE FAINGATA’A ONGO MAI ‘ENE LEA HA’U KIA AU ‘A KO E ‘OKU MAFASIA HA’U MO HO KAVENGA HA’U ‘O MA’U TA’E HA TOTONGI ‘AONGA KI HO’O MO’UI \n\n TAU FOKI MAI {×2} FOKI MAI A TAMA TUKU A HO’O POTO HA’U HE’ ENE KEI ‘AHO FOKI MAI A {×2} FOKI MAI A TAMA ‘OUA ‘E TOLOI VAVE MAI ‘A E PO’ULI"),
    Book(
        number: "278",
        title: 'HIKI ‘ETAU FONONGA ‘I MAMANI',
        content:
            "1. HIKI ‘ETAU FONONGA ‘I MAMANI KO E TOAFA ‘O E MAMAHI SIO KIMU’A KI HE KOLOSI KO SISU KALAISI \n\n 2. KUO PAU KE VETE ‘E HE MATE ‘A HOTAU FALE KELEKELE NA’A HOKO MAI ‘A E LOMI NGAUE KA TAU TEU PE \n\n 3. ‘OKU ‘UNU MAI HA ‘AHO PEHE ‘E HOKO KA KUO TA MAVAE TUTUKU ‘I HE NOFO TAIMI E HU ‘O MA’U ‘A E PALE \n\n TAU ‘OKU ‘I AI HA KOLOFUNGANI TU’UTAI KUO TEUTEU ‘E HE’ETAU TAMAI KO IA ‘E TEU TENE LAVA KI AI ‘O NOFO MO E TAMAI"),
    Book(
        number: "279",
        title: 'KO HAI ‘OKU NE ‘ILO KIAI',
        content:
            "1. KA KO HAI ‘OKU NE ‘ILO KI AI NA’A KO HA FAKA’OSI TA’U E KI SI’ETAU MO’UI NI PEA TA LAKA ATU KI KAUVAI \n\n 2. ‘E SISU MALO HO’O ‘OFA HO’O TAKI MAI ‘A E FONONGA ‘O TA LAVA MAI KI HE TA’U NI KA KUO TO SI’I KAUNGA FONONGA \n\n TAU KO E NOFO TUTUKU E KO E NOFO MAVAE PE ‘OKU HA’U ‘A E ‘AHO KENE VETEKI ‘A E NOFO NI PEA TAU MALOLO"),
    Book(
        number: "280",
        title: 'KA MATANGIA ‘A E MO’UI NI',
        content:
            "1. KA MATANGIA ‘A E MO’UI NI HE PEAU TA ‘O TAIMI PEA KA MANATU’I ‘A E TAHI KALELI ‘OUA ‘E FAKATU’ATAMAKI ‘O KA FA’AKI MAI TANUMAKI PE ‘O TUI, TUI KI HOTAU ‘OTUA \n\n 2. LAHI ‘A E FEINGA MAI ‘A E FILI KEU TO TAFIA ‘I VAHA KA NE ‘OUA ‘EIKI ‘A HO’O FOLOFOLA HAKE MAI ‘I HOKU LOTO ‘OKU TA KAUNGA O HE TELE’A ‘O E MO’UI NI ‘I HE ‘AHO PEA MO E PO \n\n 3. ‘E SISU PUKENIMA AU KEU MANATU HO’O PEKIA MA’AKU PEA KE FILI AU KEU MUIMUI KI HO’O FEKAU PEA NGAUE PE MA’AKU SISU TEU FALALA ATU KI HO’O PEKIA HE ‘AKAU"),
    Book(
        number: "281",
        title: 'KAUNGA FONONGA KI HE LANGI',
        content:
            "1. KAUNGA FONONGA KI HE LANGI ‘OUA ‘E ILIFIA ‘IMANUELA ‘OKU TAKI MOU LAKA FIEFIA \n\n 2. MAVAVA ‘A E KAU ‘ANGELO MO E HOSITE ‘O LANGI ‘A E KAU MA’ATA KOFU HINEHINA MO MASANI \n\n 3. PE TEU ‘I AI MO E FIEFIA PE KO E LO’IMATA FONU ‘A E MALIE ‘O MAMANI ‘OKU ‘O ‘IMANUELA \n\n TAU FANGAILUPE LA’A KE TOO KO FE HA POTU TEU ‘I AI ‘ANAUA E SI’OKU LOTO PE TAU FONUA ‘AFE"),
    Book(
        number: "282",
        title: 'NOFO ‘OU FAKAKAUKAU ATU',
        content:
            "1. NOFO ‘OU FAKAKAUKAU ATU SISU HO’O FEILAULAU TAUMAIA KO E SILIVA PE KOULA ‘EIKI KO HO TA’ATA’A ‘IO ‘E NGALO NAI HE HA ‘OFA PEHE ‘OFA TU’UNGA’A TAUMAIA KOHA FANONGO TALANOA KO ’EKU LEA KO E A’USIA \n\n TAU PULE MAI KEU ‘ALU HA FEITU’U PE HAKE HE MO’UNGA HIFO HE TELE’A KEHE PE KE ONGO MAI HO’O LE’O SISU KUO U TUKULOLO \n\n 2. LAHI E TAIMI ‘EKU FIFILI PE NA’E TONU KOA ‘EKU LAKA TOKI MAHINO MAI ‘OKU HALA ‘ATA KOU PEHE NI KO HO ‘OFA KO E HA NAI ‘AKU ‘E FAI TALA’EHAI ‘E LAVA KEU FETONGI TUKU A KEU HIVA KI MAMANI FAKAOFO HO’O KELESI"),
    Book(
        number: "283",
        title: 'TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI',
        content:
            "1. TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI ‘OKU MO’UI TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI ‘OKU MO’UI KEKE ‘UNU’UNU KI AI PEA NE ‘UNU’UNU MAI TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI ‘OKU MO’UI \n\n TAU HALELU’IA, HALELU’IA KO SISU TENE TOE FOKI MAI {TENE TOE FOKI MAI} HALELU’IA, HALELU’IA KO SISU TENE TOE FOKI MAI \n\n 2. TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI ‘OKU MO’ONI ......... \n\n 3. TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI ‘OKU ‘OFA ......... \n\n 4. TOE ALA MAI ‘A E ‘EIKI ‘OKU IKUNA .........."),
    Book(
        number: "284",
        title: '‘EIKI SISU HO’O ‘OFA',
        content:
            "SOLO: 1. ‘EIKI SISU HO’O ‘OFA, HE’IKAI TOE LAVA ‘E TAHA KO KOE PE SISU E MONU’IA \n\n TENOA: 2. ’OFA HULU FAU E MO MATE FAKALONGO PE SISU E ALAMAI KI HOKU LOTO KEU ONGO’I HO’O LAUMALIE \n\n KATOA: 3. LILINGI HO’O ‘OFA ‘IATE AU ‘EIKI KOE HIA PE KO KITA ANGE FAU TA’ETAAU VIVILI KEU LAVA’I ‘A HEVANI KOLO FO’OU FAKA’OFO’OFA FAU MO MASANI (MASANI)"),
    Book(
        number: "285",
        title: 'TALANOA ‘EHE FOLOFOLA',
        content:
