        title: 'SKIT TOETU’U – SIONE 20: 1 – 18',
        content:
            "‘OKU MAU FIEFIA KE TALITALI KIMOUTOLU {KATOA} KAU ‘APITANGA MO E KAINGA KOTOA \n\n FOKOTU’U TELINGA MAI PEA OMI KIATE AU {KATOA} FAKAFANONGO KAE MO’UI HO LAUMALIE \n\n KO E ‘ULUAKI ‘AHO ‘ENI ‘O E UIKE {KATOA} KUO UHU ‘A MELE KI FONUALOTO PEA NE TOKANGA’I HE’ENE VAKAI TA KOE MAKA ‘ENA KUO TEKA’I \n\n ‘OIAUE KUO TEKA’I E MAKAKAFU {MELE} ‘OIAUE KO HAI ENI KUO NE FAI KIATE AU. \n\n NA’A NE LELE LEVA ‘O TALA KIA SAIMONE PITA {KATOA} MOE AKONGA NA’E ‘OFA TAHA AI ‘A E MISAIA. \n\n KUO NAU ‘AVE ‘A E ‘EIKI MEI HE FONUALOTO {MELE} PEA ‘OKU ’IKAI TEU ‘ILO PE KUO NAU TUKU IA KI FE \n\n MA’A NA LELE, NA’A NA LELE {KATOA} KA NA’E OMA ANGE ‘A E AKO ‘E TAHA NA’A NE A’U PE ‘O TU’U PE ‘I TU’A ‘PEA NE PUNOU ‘ONE SIO PE KI LOTO \n\n KO E NGAAHI TUPENU PE {AKONGA} ‘OKU OU SIO KI AI OKU TUKU MAI. \n\n KA KO PITA, KA KO PITA {KATOA} NA’A NE MOLE PE KI FONUALOTO ‘ONE MO’U VAKAIA KI HONO ‘E’EPA’ANGA ‘ENE HA NGALI KEHE MO FAKAILIFIA. \n\n VAKAI ATU A KI HE FATUFATU KEHE {PITA} ‘A E NGAAHI TUPENU NA \n\n KO AU IA ‘A E ‘ULUAKI FAKAMO’ONI {AKONGA} KUO TOETU’U ‘A HOTAU ‘EIKI NA’A NE FOLOFOLA PE ‘E HOLO ‘AHO TOLU PE PEA NE TOE LANGA E FALE. \n\n NA’A NA FOKI PE KI ‘API………………………………….. {KATOA} KA E TU’U TANGI PE ‘A MELE HE VE’E FONUALOTO. NA’A NE VAKAI ATU TA KO E ONGO ANGELO ‘ENA OKU FOTU MAI \n\n FEFINE KO E HA KUO KE TANGI AI…………………… {ANGELO} \n\n KUO NAU ‘AVE HOKU ‘EIKI……………………………… {MELE} ‘OKU ‘IKAI TEU ‘ILO PE ‘OKU NAU TUKU IA ‘I FE \n\n FEFINE KO E HA KUO KE TANGI AI…………………… {SISU} KO HAI ‘OKU KE KUMI \n\n KAPAU KO KOE IA NA’A KE ‘AVE………………………. {MELE} TALAMAI MU’A KAU ‘AVE IA ‘E AU ‘E MELE…………………………………………………….. {SISU} LAPONAI E …………………………………………………. {MELE} HALELU’IA KO E MATAPA NA’E SILA’I ………………. {KATOA} KUO TO’O PE ‘E HE MAFI \n\n ‘OUA TEKE ALA MAI KIATE AU……………………….. {SISU} HE ‘OKU TE’EKI KEU ‘ALU KI HE TAMAI KA KE ALU ‘O TALA ‘A E ME’A KUO KE MAMATA KI AI. \n\n SISU KO E TU’I ‘O E NGAAHI TU’I……………… {FAKAMA’OPO’OPO} KUO NE IKUNA ‘A FA’ITOKA HE KO E TU’I ‘O E NGAAHI TU’I ‘E PUNOU PE KI AI PEA KALANGA KOTOA PE KO SISU KO E TU’I ‘O E NGAAHI TU’I."),
    Book(
        number: "304",
        title: 'TUKU KE FAKAHAOFI AU MEI HELI',
        content:
            "1. TUKU KE FAKAHAOFI AU MEI HELI ‘OU TU’U HE MATAPA ‘O HEVANI ‘O FAKALANGILANGI ‘OFA KUO KE FAI HIVA FAKAFETA’I {Katoa} \n\n TAU ‘OU VIKIA (‘OU VIKIA) HO HUAFA (HO HUAFA) HO HUAFA TAPUHA HOKU TU’I (HOKU TU’I) HOKU ‘EIKI (HOKU ‘EIKI) ‘E LAU ‘ITANITI KO IA TEU HIVA, HIVA, HIVA, HIVA, HIVA. HO HUAFA ‘OU VIKIA HO HUAFA, HO HUAFA ‘OU VIKIA HO HUAFA, HO HUAFA \n\n 2. MONU E KUO MAHINO MAI KAVEINGA ‘EKU NOFO MAMANI TEU TUKUPA KEU FOAKI ‘A ‘EKU MO’UI KO HO FAKALANGILANGI {Katoa}"),
    Book(
        number: "305",
        title: 'NA’E ALU TOKUA (FOHA MAUMAU KOLOA)',
        content:
            "1. NA’E ‘ALU TOKUA HA TANGATA KO E KUMI ‘ENE FIEFIA PEA ‘OSI ‘ENE KOLOA PEA NOFO HE ‘A PUAKA \n\n 2. PEA TU’U LEVA IA KE NE FOKI KE NE FOKI KI HONO ‘API PEA ‘ILO MAI ‘E HE TAMAI ‘AUE ‘ENE LELE MAI \n\n 3. PEA ‘ITA ‘A E FOHA LAHI KA E TALA ‘E HE ‘OTUA HA’U EE KAU FA’ITELIHA HONO TUFA ‘A ‘EKU ‘OFA \n\n TAU TEU FOKI NAI TEU FOKI NAI ‘OKU ‘OFA MAI ‘EKU TAMAI TEU FOKI NAI TEU FOKI NAI ‘OKU ‘OFA MAI ‘EKU TAMAI \n\n ‘OKU TALI ‘A E FAKATOMALA"),
    Book(
        number: "306",
        title: 'FAKAMO’UI MAHAKI',
        content:
            "KE FANONGO MAI ‘A E FAKATAHA NI………………. {FAKAAFE} KAU LEA KI HE ‘OFA NE FAI KO E ‘OFA ‘A LANGI KI HONO KAKAI PE TETA KAU AI PE ‘IKAI \n\n FEKUMI MAI ‘A E TAUHI SIPI LELEI………………….. {KATOA} ‘ILO’I ‘A E SIPI ‘IKAI HANO TAUHI TONU PE KE NE HANGA ‘O LI’AKI KA NA’A NE UI IA \n\n MUIMUI MAI KIATE AU………………………………….. {SISU} MUIMUI MAI KIATE AU \n\n SISU E MALO HO’O ‘OFA……………………………….. {SIPI MOLE} LAVE AI AU KO E ANGAHALA ‘OU MA’U AI HO’O ‘ALO’OFA NOFO HE NONGA ‘A E ‘AFIO NA \n\n KO E TA’U ‘ENI ‘E 38……………………………………… {HEKE} MO ‘EKU HEKE HOLO HE VE’EHALA KA KO LOTO HA TOKOTAHA KE TOKONI HE FAINGATA’A KA KO SISU NA’A NE FEKAU AU KEU TU’U ‘O TO’O HOKU MOHENGA \n\n TU’U PE TO’O HO’O MOHENGA………………………… {SISU} PEA KE HA’ELE \n\n HALELU’IA……………………………………………………. {HEKE} \n\n HALELU’IA KUOU HAO ‘I HONO TA’ATA’A……………. {KATOA} NEU ‘AUHIA HIFO HE MATE TA’ENGATA KA KUOU HAO HE’ENE ‘OFA \n\n KO E KUI AI MO KOLEKOLE {KUI} HOLO PE ‘I HE VE’EHALA NA’A KU FANONGO KI HA TOKOTAHA NE FONONGA HAKE HE LOTO HALA TA KO SISU KO E ‘ALO KO E PELE ‘A E ‘OTUA TALU AI ‘ENE KAIKAILA…………………………………… {KATOA} \n\n SISU E HAKO ‘O TEVITA………………………………….. {KUI} NGAOHI ANGE MU’A AU KEU ‘A NGAOHI AU KEU MAMATA \n\n HALELU’IA……………………………………………………. {HEKE} \n\n HALELU’IA KUOU HAO ‘I HONO TA’ATA’A……………. {KATOA} NEU ‘AUHIA HIFO HE MATE TA’ENGATA KA KUOU HAO HE’ENE ‘OFA \n\n NA’A NAU TAKI IA KI TU’A’A……………………………… {KATOA} KE FAI HONO TOLOMAKA KA KO SISU NA’A NE ‘I AI ‘O FAI HONO FAKAHAOFI \n\n ‘ILONGA PE ‘A KO E ‘OKU HAOHAOA…………………. {SISU} KEKE FUA FAI MU’A E TOLOMAKA \n\n TALU AI ‘ENA PULI TAHA………………………………… {KATOA} ‘OSI AI MO ‘ENAU FAKAANGA \n\n SISU E KE KE TAUKAPO’I AU…………………………... {ANGAHALA} NEONGO ‘EKU MO’UI TA’ETAAU KA TEU PIKI ATU PE KI HO ‘AKAU KE KE FAKAMA’A ‘A E HIA KO AU. \n\n HALELU’IA……………………………………………………. {ANGAHALA} \n\n HALELU’IA KUOU HAO ‘I HONO TA’ATA’A……………. {KATOA} NEU ‘AUHIA HIFO HE MATE TA’ENGATA KA KUOU HAO HE’ENE ‘OFA \n\n FIE FANONGO MU’A KI HE UI {FAKAMA’OPO’OPO} SISU ‘ENA, OKU TUKITUKI FAKAAVA HOTAU LOTO KAE HU MAI KE TAU NONOFO"),
    Book(
        number: "307",
        title: 'SISU FAKAFETA’I KI HO’O UI',
        content:
            "1. SISU FAKAFETA’I KI HO’O UI LAHI E TAIMI KUO U MAUMAU’I VAKAI KI HE KUOHILI ‘O E MO’UI NI KO KOE PE ‘IO ‘EIKI NE KE TOKONI \n\n 2. KO KOE PE ‘A E MALU’ANGA ‘O E FONONGA NEONGO PE ‘A E FAINGATA’A ‘O E HALA KAU FALALA KI HE ‘AFIONA KAU NONGA KO E HALA IA KI HE MO’UI TA’ENGATA. \n\n 3. LAHI TA’U HO’O TAUHI KIATE AU FAKALEKESI ‘EKU MO’UI KEU TAAU KAU HOLI ‘EIKI KE KE MA’U ATU HA MO’UI NE ‘I MALA KUO LUVA ATU. \n\n TAU SISU KO HAI, KO HAI AU KE KE HAMUSI AU MEI HE PALAKU TALUNGA MO HO’O ‘OFA TA’EMALAU KEU LAVE AI ‘EKU MO’UI TA’ETAAU"),
    Book(
        number: "308",
        title: 'NE TAUANGA’A ‘A NATULA',
        content:
            "1. NE TAUANGA’A ‘A NATULA MO E FUNGA E FONUA PULONGA AI MO E TALONI TOPUTAPU E ‘OTUA KO SELUSALEMA KO E KOLO HAU KUO LUSA KO E TU’I MO HONO KAKAI KUO NAU TEUAKI KO E PELE ‘O LANGI KUO NAU PUKE ‘I KETISEMANI \n\n 2. NE FAKAMAAU ‘IA PONITUSI PAILATO FAI AI HONO ‘ANUHIA KAE ‘IKAI KE HANU KO HAI ‘IA SISU MO PALAPASA ‘E HAO MOU FAITELIHA AA MU’A ‘I HONO TUKIFA’O KAE ‘OMI AA MU’A KIA AU ‘A E VAI FANOFANO \n\n TAU SEUKE ‘A HONO TAKI ATU KE KALUSEFAI SEUKE ‘A HONO MANUKI’I MO TAUKAE’I NE NAU HIKI KI ‘OLUNGA ‘O TUTUKI HE ‘AKAU KAE FAKALONGOLONGO PE ‘O ‘IKAI KE LEA PE HANU \n\n 3. LEA FAKA-LOMA, FAKA-HEPELU MO FAKA-KALISI PEA HIKI HA LEA KI AI KO HONO LEA MANUKI SISU ‘ENA KO E PILINISI SIU FIE TU’I NE PA ‘A E MANA PEA TAPA MO E FATULISI KO ‘ATONAI SIHOVA E KUO NE MAFULI \n\n 4. ‘ILAI ‘ILAI LAMA SAPAKATANAI HIKI HONO LE’O ‘O FAKAFOA MO E TANGI KO E HA KUO KE LI’AKI AI AU ‘E TAMAI KA KOHO FINANGALO KE FAKALAKA ‘A E IPU ‘IA AU ‘OUA NA’A FAI HOKU LOTO FAI HO FINANGALO"),
    Book(
        number: "309",
        title: 'FAKAFETA’I KIA SIHOVA {Saame 107:1,9,43}',
        content:
            "TAU FAKAFETA’I KIA SIHOVA HE ‘OKU LELEI IA HE ‘OKU TOLONGA ‘O TA’ENGATA ‘ENE ‘ALO’OFA. \n\n 1. HE ‘OKU NE FAKAMAKONA ‘A E LAUMALIE HOLI PEA KO E LOTO ‘OKU FIEKAIA ‘OKU NE FAKAPITO ‘I HE LELEI \n\n 2. ‘ILONGA HA POTO TE NE TOKANGA’I ‘A E NGAAHI ME’A NI PEA ‘E ‘UHINGA KIATE KINAUTOLU ‘A E ‘ALO’OFA ‘A E ‘EIKI"),
    Book(
        number: "310",
        title: '‘EKI SISU ‘OFA E',
        content:
            "1. ‘EIKI SISU OFA E FANONGOA ‘EKU TO’E TO’E MO TANGI KIATE KOE TUKU MAI HO LAUMALIE \n\n 2. TUKU KEU POLETAKI NEONGO E FILI MO E ‘AHI’AHI TEU FALALA KIATE KOE ‘ATONAI KEHE HO FINANGALO KEU FAI \n\n TAU TUKU ‘EIKI KEU TO’A KEU FEPAKI MO E FAINGATA’A TEU PIKI HO FOLOFOLA (solo) KO IA PE ‘A E FOUNGA \n\n 3. PEAUA E FONONGA’ANGA TEVOLO MO ‘ENE FOUNGA KA TEU UNGA HO FATAFATA KO KOE HOKU MAKATU’UNGA"),
    Book(
        number: "311",
        title: 'FAKAFETA’I',
        content:
            "TAU FAKAFETA’I, FAKAFETA’I KUO IKUNA ‘A KALEVALE FAKAFETA’I, FAKAFETA’I ‘EIKI SISU E KUOU FIEMALIE \n\n 1. NOFO HA’ISIA ‘I HE ‘AHO KOTOA FIHIA HE TAUHELE ‘A SETANE FONU FAINGATA’A ‘O E FONONGA KAE TALUNGA MO SISU ‘ENE PEKIA AAAA \n\n 2. ‘EIKI KUOU HAO PE ‘I HO’O ‘OFA MO’UI NI NE TAUMU’A VALEA LOKA HE FILI MA’U POPULA ‘OKU KE FAKATAU’ATAINA TAU’ATAINA"),
    Book(
        number: "312",
        title: 'SISU KEU INU ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’UI',
        content:
            "1. SISU KEU INU ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’UI SISU KEU INU ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’UI SISU KEU INU ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’U KOUNA AU KEU INU [solo] KOUNA AU KEU LATA [oloto KOUNA AU KEU TALI [tenoa & laulalo] \n\n 2. SISU TEU LATA ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’UI SISU TEU LATA ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’UI SISU TEU LATA ‘I HE VAI ‘O E MO’U KOUNA AU KEU INU [solo] KOUNA AU KEU LATA [oloto] KOUNA AU KEU TALI [tenoa & laulalo] \n\n 3. SISU KUOU TALI ‘A E VAI ‘O E MO’UI SISU KUOU TALI ‘A E VAI ‘O E MO’UI SISU KUOU TALI ‘A E VAI ‘O E MO’U KOUNA AU KEU INU [solo] KOUNA AU KEU LATA [oloto KOUNA AU KEU TALI [katoa]"),
    Book(
        number: "313",
        title: '‘ALO’OFA MAI SISU KI HE’EKU HU (LOTU)',
        content:
            "1. ‘ALO’OFA MAI SISU KI HE’EKU HU KO E LAMI ‘ENA HOMAU MOIHU ‘EMAU TAUTAPA TAMAI HOMAI FAKAU HE KUO MAU TAFIA HE PEAU HELENGALU \n\n 2. ‘EIKI KUO MALA’IA E FUNGA FONUA NI HAVALA HE PA’ANGA FE’AUAKI E KAKAI ‘OKU MAU LOTU LAUMALIE HIFO MAI HA MEESI KE MONU’IA E ‘OTU TONGA NI \n\n 3. ‘E TOLONA PE LOA MO E FAINGATA’A KAPAU TE TAU FOKI KI HE UHO’I MAAMA KO E TUHULU MO E KAPASA HE FAINGATA’A ‘OKU NE VETEKINA ‘ETAU MAFASIA’ANGA \n\n TAU SISU LANU AU ‘I HO TA’ATA’A HE KELESI KEI MAPUNA ‘I VAIOLA KO E FANGUMALINGI SI’I FOFONGA ‘OFA PIKIPIKI KATEA HE KOLOSI FAKALAVA"),
    Book(
        number: "314",
        title: '‘OI SI’ETE NOFO NI  (‘EVANGELIO)',
        content:
            "1. ‘OI SI’ETE NOFO NI ‘I HE POTU LALA MO’UI NI PO’ULIA ‘IKAI KITE HA MAAMA LUSA HE FE’AUAKI HOKU ‘ANGA’ANGA MATE’ANGA ‘ENI ‘O E TO’UTANGATA \n\n 2. KO HAI ‘OKU UI ‘OKU MUIMUI MAI ‘ONE ‘ILO ‘EKU TO’E TOFANGA HE MAMAHI KO AU SAMALETANI TU’U KETA FOKI HE KO SISU ‘ENA KEI TAUTAU HE KOLOSI \n\n 3. NEKE SITU’A MEIATE AU KAU TANGI TOUPILI HE KO ‘EKU PELE KOE ‘EKU NGOUE LOSE FOKI MAI TAMA TUI E KALAUNI E KETA ‘EVANGELIO KI MO’UNGA KALEVALE \n\n TAU KO E HIA NI KUO MOLE KOTOA ANGAHALA AU KUOU FAKATOMALA MALO SISU HO’O ‘OFA LAULOTAHA KI HE HIAMATEA NI KI HE MO’UI TA’ENGATA."),
    Book(
        number: "315",
        title: 'TEU HOLA KI FE MEI HE ‘AHO LAHI',
        content:
            "1. TEU HOLA KI FE MEI HE ‘AHO LAHI TEU FOKI PE ‘O UI ‘EIKI E TALI MAI KO E HIAMATEA AU TEU TO’E MO TANGI FUA AU ‘EIKI FUFU TUMUAKI HO KOLOSI \n\n 2. KO E FILI ‘ENA MA TAKANGA HE ‘AHO KO SETANE ‘OKU LALATA HE TU’APO FAFANGU KEU INU HE IFO MO VOVO KO E MATE’ANGA IA HOTAU ‘AHO \n\n 3. KO SISU ‘ENA KEI TU’U ‘O TALI KI HA ‘AHO TEKE FOKI MAI KI HE ‘EIKI ‘IKAI TEU ‘EKE HA PA’ANGA PE TOTONGI HE KOE PELE KOE NEU TALAKI KI AI. \n\n TAU FUFU AU SISU KEU PULI FUFU AI SISU KEU MO’UI TANU HOKU MALA HO FOFONGA ‘OFA KAU PALUTU HE VAIOLA HO TA’ATA’A."),
    Book(
        number: "316",
        title: 'KUO MATANGIA E MO’UI (FOKI KI HE KOLOSI)',
        content:
            "1. KUO MATANGIA E MO’UI HE TOAFA’ONE HE HOLI ‘A E LOTO MAMANI MO HONO TAUELE KE FAKATU’UMALIE ‘ENE FILI HE KO E PELE KO E MATE KUOPAU IKU KI HE MATE PE \n\n 2. TAMA TOKANGA HE KO SETANE ‘ENA TENE VELE’I KEKE KA’ANGA PEA TOKI HOLA KA KUO KE HE ‘O ‘IKAI ‘ILO HO ‘ALUNGA KO E MANUKIA’ANGA ‘O E TO’UTANGATA. \n\n 3. HA’U KIA SISU KO E FALE MAAMA TE NE TULI PEA SE’E TEVOLO E TOAFA KA KE FONONGA FIEFIA HE HALA FAINGATA’A ‘O ‘A’EVA KI HE HEVANI MO HONO MAKAKOLOA \n\n TAU KO TOAFA ‘ENA ‘OKU TALI MAI MO MATE KO TOAFA ‘ENA ‘OKU TALI MAI KA KOE FAI LEVA HO FILI ‘O FOKI KI HE ‘EIKI FAI LEVA HO FILI FOKI KI HE KOLOSI"),
    Book(
        number: "317",
        title: 'MOLE ‘A E KOULA ( HIVA SAPATE FA’E)',
        content:
            "1. MOLE ‘A E KOULA E NOFO TAIMI SI’EKU FA’E FOFONGA ‘OFA NEU FAKALEKESI TEU LAULOTOA KO FOTUNGA FOTU MALIMALI KO E VAIKAU’AKI ‘EKU PILIKIMI FAKALANGI \n\n 2. FAKAPO E FA’E MATE KO AU KA KO SISU ‘ENA KO E PUNUNGA MALU SAPATE FA’E LO’IMATA’IA MO’UI MANATU HE FA NE ‘ALAHA ‘O MAPAKI KEI NGANGATU \n\n TAU ALA MAI SISU HIKI AU KI ‘OLUNGA HE KO E FA’E MATE AU PAEA LI’EKINA TAKI HOKU HALA FAKAAVA ‘A E MATAPA KEU HU ‘OU MALU ‘I HE TA’ATA’A KEI LELEPA \n\n 3. ‘ALA SI’EKU TAMA TUKU E TANGI MAMAHI HE KO E MAAMA ‘ENI ‘O E NUNU MO ‘OSI FOKI KI HE ‘EIKI TOKANGA KI HE’ENE UI HE KO E FA’E FITA IA ‘O E KUONGA NI."),
    Book(
        number: "318",
        title: 'FANONGO MAI ( UI MEI HEVANI)',
        content:
            "1. FANONGO MAI LE’O UI HEVANI E KO ‘EKU LUPE ‘ENA ‘I KALEVALE TU’U ‘O ULUI ‘ALAA SI’EKU PELE HA’U A SI’EKU KOLOA NE MOLE \n\n 2. HA’U ‘O ULUI FANONGO KI HE UI ‘OUA ‘E TAPUNI PE FAKAONGO TULI KO AU SISU ‘OKU OU TUKITUKI TO’O KIA AU KO HO ‘EIKI HUHU’I \n\n 3. KO AU ‘ENI TULUTUI ‘O HANGA HAKE SISU E SI’O PEKIA ’I KALEVALE MA ‘A E MO’UI NI TONU KI HE MATE KA KUOU LAU KO HO TISAIPALE \n\n TAU HA’U A TAMA ‘O ULUI HA’U A FANONGO KI HE UI FAKATOMALA HA’U A ‘O TUI KIA SISU KALAISI KO E KOTO MO’UI."),
    Book(
        number: "319",
        title: 'MO’UI NI PUPUTU’U (MATANGIVALE MO’UI)',
        content:
            "1. MO’UI NI PUPUTU’U HE KUO TO E TAUFA TOLONA E TAULA FESI MO E AFA TU’ANAKI ‘AUKA E MO’UI ‘O NOFO LELENGA KO E MATE KUOPAU HOKU IKU’ANGA \n\n 2. TEU LUSIA PE KI TAULANGA HA NONGA KE KUMI HA KELESI FAKAFOLOFOLA KE NE FUFULU ‘EKU MO’UI FAKALIELIA TAFOKI MAI TAMA KI HE LAMI ‘AVE HIA \n\n 3. FAKATAULAMA AU SISU MEI HE MATE KEU FOKI ‘O LAU AU KO HO PELE TA KO E NONGA ‘OUA FALALA HE KOLOA KO E MATANGIA’ANGA ‘O E TO’UTANGATA \n\n TAU ‘EIKI SISU, SISU, SISU E HA’U ‘O TOKONI, HA’U KE TA FEOHI PE KO E MO’UI NI KUO MATANGI VALE FAKAOLA HE TA’ATA’A NE TOULIKI ‘I KALEVALE."),
    Book(
        number: "320",
        title: 'KO E ONGOONGO FAKALOLOMA (FALAITE LELEI)',
        content:
            "1. KO E ONGOONGO FAKALOLOMA HENGIHENGI FALAITE ‘O E PEKIA SI’I SISU ‘ENA HAKO ‘O TEVITA KUO NE PEKIA ‘I HE FUNGA MO’UNGA \n\n 2. ‘OI FAKAPO SI’ONO TUKI FA’O NE HOKA TAOA PE KA E SI’I LONGO ‘AU’AUHIA PE SI’ONO LO’IMATA ‘O INU FIEMALIE E IPU MALA \n\n 3. TAMA HA’U A KE TA FAKATOMALA KE FAKAHOUNGA’I SI’ENE ‘OFA HE KO E TOKONI KEI LELEPA KO E HUFANGA’ANGA ‘O E KUONGA \n\n TAU MALO SISU ‘A HO’O ‘OFA HO’O TO’O ‘A ‘EKU HIA KEU HU ATU HO PULE’ANGA ‘OU MALO ‘I HO NIMA ‘OFA"),
    Book(
        number: "321",
        title: 'KO E ONGOONGO NI (KAVA MALOHI TAPU)',
        content:
            "1. KO E ONGOONGO NI ‘OSI HONO MATUA’I ‘A E KAVA MALOHI MAUMAU ‘OKU FAI TAMATE MO VETEKI FAMILI TOKOLAHI KO E LUSA’ANGA TO’UTUPU ‘O E SIASI \n\n 2. ‘OUA TEKE HANGANOA HONO HU’AMELIE HE KO E LAIONE TAKAFIA HE KOLOPE ‘OKU NE VILO TAKAI FAKASAIKOLONE ‘O FAKAULUI TANGATA MA’A SETANE \n\n 3. TAMA TUKU E MO’UI FA’A KONA HE TE KE POLEPOLE HE MO’UI FAKALUSA HA’U KIA SISU KA KE MA’U ‘A E NONGA TE NE TAKI KO E KI HE MO’UI TA’ENGATA \n\n TAU HOLA LEVA KE VAVE ‘OUA TE KE ALA FAKA’EHI’EHI E MO’UI TELIA ‘A MALA KA KE HOLA SIO MA’U KI HE NGATA PALASA NE HIKI KI ‘OLUNGA HE ‘AKAU FAKALAVA."),
    Book(
        number: "322",
        title: 'HIVA HALELU’IA HIVA KIA SIHOVA',
        content:
            "1. HIVA HALELU’IA HIVA KIA SIHOVA TA E HA’APE MO HIVA KALANGA HE KO E HELO ‘OTUA PEA TAPUHA HAU TA’ELIUA ‘O SIHOVA SIAILA \n\n 2. KO IA KO E MAFI TO’A HE FEPAKI HE KO SATAI TU’I MAFIMAFI TEU KALANGA PEA KAILAVAKI ‘A E MAFI ‘O SIHOVA SAPAOTI \n\n 3. HOSANA ‘O KALANGA KIA ‘IMANUELA KO E TU’I ‘O E ‘OFA FAKALEVELEVA NE TUKU E MASANI MO E KOLOLIA HIFO HE KOLOSI KE NE PEKIA \n\n TAU HIKI MAVAVA HEILALA ‘O LANGI KUO FAKALANGA HE ‘OFA TU’UTAI SISU KO E LAMI SISU KALUSEFAI KO E ‘EIKI MISAIA ‘O MAMANI."),
    Book(
        number: "323",
